&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in finance, accounting or related field. (Required)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ten (10) or more years of progressive finance (FP&amp;amp;A) and accounting experience (Required)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in healthcare, specifically Value-Based Care and Medicare (Strongly Preferred)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in Windows-based computer applications; Advanced proficiency with Microsoft Excel (Required)&lt;/li&gt;
