&lt;li&gt;Provide functional and technical support for Oracle Financials and Oracle EPM Cloud applications, including ARCS, EPBCS, and EDMCS.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support Oracle EPM processes including account reconciliations, transaction matching, planning and budgeting cycles, forecasting, reporting, metadata management, hierarchy maintenance, data governance, and integration support.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Accounting and Finance teams to support ARCS processes including reconciliation compliance, profiles, formats, match types, data loads, period close activities, dashboards, reporting, and issue resolution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Financial Planning &amp;amp; Analysis teams to support EPBCS processes including planning forms, business rules, calculations, data maps, reporting, security, scenario/version management, and annual budget and forecast cycles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support EDMCS processes including enterprise metadata governance, hierarchy and dimension management, request workflows, subscriptions, mappings, validations, and integrations with Oracle Financials, EPM, and downstream systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support and understand integrations in and out of Oracle Financials and Oracle EPM applications, including data loads, extracts, metadata integrations, automation processes, and reconciliation between source and target systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead and facilitate business analysis and requirements development and management processes, including eliciting, documenting, analyzing, modeling, prioritizing, validating, and tracing requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
