&lt;li&gt;Leverage AI tools to accelerate and automate testing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with cross-functional teams to integrate products with business processes and backend infrastructure.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work on a variety of products, demonstrating flexibility and adaptability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure the scalability, performance, and security of developed solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in code reviews, contributing to and maintaining high code quality.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay up-to-date with emerging technologies and industry best practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
