&lt;li&gt;Four (4) or more years of software development experience and/or a reviewable portfolio of work.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of software development principles and best practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with testing platforms such as Selenium and Playwright&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent problem-solving and communication skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work independently and collaboratively in a fast-paced environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with Front End technology like REACT and NextJS.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with Back End development of APIs and data structures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in the Healthcare industry.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with HL7, FHIR, or other healthcare data standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
